window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In the Atlantic Ocean, north of the Caribbean Sea, there are waters of legend. Three points serve as the boundaries of these waters - the southern tip of Florida, the island of Puerto Rico, and the mid-Atlantic island of Bermuda. This is the Bermuda Triangle.</p> <p>Throughout history, many ships and planes have mysteriously gone missing in these cursed tides. What dark thing resides there?</p> <p>One year after the events of <i>A Ghost of Fire</i>, newly married Steve and Katie Nicholas are about to find out the answer to one of the ocean's darkest mysteries.</p> <p>But will they make it out together?</p>"; 
